MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 55/1/1/73 CF
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA(BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SEOCRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACH IVA LAYA)
Department of Cabinet Affairs (Mantrimandal Karya Vibhag)
New Delhi, 23 July 1973.
1 Sravana 1895.
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect
from July 23, 1973,
(i) Shrimati Indira Gandhi, Prime Minister(Pradhan Mantri)
relinquished the office of the Minister of Steel and
Mines(Ispat aur Khan Ma ntri); and
(ii) Shri T.A. Pai, Minister of Heavy Industry (Bhari
Udyog Mantri) shall hold temporarily the additional
charge of the Ministry of Steel and Mines(Ispat
aur Khan Mantralaya).
(R. N. Kalia
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Mombers of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Members, Planning Commission,
for information.
Copy forwarded to:-
Secretary to the Prime Minister (Pradhan Mantri ke Sachiv).
Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister (Pradhan Mantri ke
Sanyukt Sachiv).
Private Secretary to the Prime Minister(Pradhan Mantri ke
Niji Sachiv).
Copy forwarded to:-
Secrotary to the President (Rashtrapati ke Sachiv).
Secretary to the Vice-President (Up-Ra shtrapati ke Sachiv).
(R.N. KaTia
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
